{
  "stem": "4513.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And anyway, so we-- they gave us-- they gave us a whole book of descriptions of German war criminals and-- that we were to look for.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They gave us all kinds of tattoos and all kinds of things they knew about these people, and that we were trying to find them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so we were-- and we were to strip search everybody we saw.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I said, Women and-- He said, anybody, you strip search.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Just be sure they have no contraband, no war contraband.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that if you find anything, you-- you-- you log it, you put it down, you describe it, you put in these boxes and send it back to us.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that's what we did for about-- about four weeks, five weeks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Awful lot of people, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you know, I asked them all the same question-- did you know about the concentration camps?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I go, why do you think about Jews?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm telling you, almost to a person, they all saw Jews as the bad people in their country.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That they are not sorry about the ones who they got rid of, that somehow or another, they shouldn't have been there in the first place.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that Jews-- they say, one day you'll-- I remember one fellow, he said, one day you'll learn that you befriend these people and you take care of them and they'll take everything you got.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because that's what they do.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he says, they will take all your resources.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They will-- and next thing you know, they will be in charge of everything and you won't have anything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I get the lecture from him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I said, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
